text: Blake Schraader (born 8 June 1994) is a South African cricketer. He made his Twenty20 debut for Mpumalanga in the 2018 Africa T20 Cup on 14 September 2018. In September 2019, he was named in Northern Cape's squad for the 2019–20 CSA Provincial T20 Cup. He made his List A debut on 24 November 2019, for Northern Cape in the 2019–20 CSA Provincial One-Day Challenge. He made his first-class debut on 28 November 2019, for Northern Cape in the 2019–20 CSA 3-Day Provincial Cup. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:South African cricketers Category:Mpumalanga cricketers Category:Northern Cape cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
